---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab Named One of the Best Supply Chain & Logistics Software Solutions by G2 in 2025 - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab earns recognition as one of G2's 2025 Best Software Award winners for Supply Chain & Logistics products."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Post-Purchase</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab Named One of the Best Supply Chain &amp; Logistics Software Solutions by G2 in 2025</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Anna Lapezo</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2025-02-18">February 18, 2025</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>7 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          parcelLab has earned recognition as one of G2's 2025 Best Software Award winners for Supply Chain &amp; Logistics products. The platform delivers impact by helping global brands enhance operational efficiency, customer communication, and post-purchase experiences.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">The Growing Demand for Best-in-Class Supply Chain Software</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Supply chain complexity continues escalating, driving leaders toward advanced technologies. By 2028, approximately 25% of KPI reporting will leverage Generative AI models. Meanwhile, 95% of data-driven decisions will be at least partially automated -- yet only 10% of CEOs report strategic AI implementation. This gap represents opportunity for logistics organizations to employ AI-driven automation and real-time tracking.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Technology investment has become a competitive necessity: 27% of supply chain leaders cite gaining competitive advantage as a top three goal for new technology investments.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">What Makes parcelLab One of the Best Logistics Software Solutions?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab extends beyond traditional tracking by enabling brands to control the post-purchase experience. The platform reduces customer inquiries and increases engagement through personalized updates, branded tracking pages, and upsell opportunities.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How parcelLab Stands Out</h2>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Seamless Order Tracking &amp; Communication</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed italic">
              "parcelLab has been helping us with communications and order tracking in a seamless manner because of which our customers receive timely updates. This has improved operations and helped create valued customer relationships."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- G2 Customer Review</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Deeper Delivery Insights</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed italic">
              "parcelLab affords us the ability to dive deeper into delivery issue reasons for customers. Using three different tools for delivery positioning, parcelLab gives the absolute best real-time information!"
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- G2 Customer Review</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Advanced Reporting &amp; Customization</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed italic">
              "The reports and metrics module are most valuable -- customizable and complete, allowing in-depth improvement of customer messages. The ability to adapt messages and make modifications quickly proves essential in emergencies."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- G2 Customer Review</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Multi-Courier Tracking</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed italic">
              "The ability to track parcels from multiple couriers simultaneously. The user interface is excellent and easy to navigate. Compared to previous systems, this platform resolves customer queries much faster."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- G2 Customer Review</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">The Future of Logistics &amp; Supply Chain Software</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Global e-commerce is projected to reach $6.8 trillion in 2025. Companies investing in supply chain optimization will better position themselves to retain customers, boost loyalty, and drive revenue growth.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How parcelLab Helps Retailers Drive Revenue &amp; Loyalty</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Reducing WISMO inquiries</strong> to lower operational costs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Enhancing post-purchase engagement</strong> with branded tracking</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Improving delivery experience</strong> through carrier performance insights</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Converting shipping into a growth driver</strong> via upsells and retention</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The G2 recognition validates parcelLab's approach to redefining the post-purchase experience. As supply chain expectations evolve, selecting the right logistics software proves essential for maintaining competitiveness and customer retention.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
